# Code Owners
# 
# This file defines who is responsible for reviewing changes to specific
# parts of the codebase. Code owners are automatically requested for review
# when someone opens a pull request that modifies code they own.
#
# Order is important; the last matching pattern takes the most precedence.
# When someone opens a pull request that only modifies files in a 
# particular directory, only the code owners for that directory will be 
# requested for review.

# Global Owners
# These owners will be requested for all changes unless a more specific rule applies
* @chrimar3

